<%# <h1>Register#register_created</h1> %>
<%= image_tag attachments['50email.png'].url, alt: 'My Photo',width: 500, class: 'photos' %>
<div class="content-letter">
  <p>Dear <%= @name %>,</p>
  <% if @guest_type == "Accompanying Delegate" %>
    <p>Thank you for registrating for the upcoming 1CISP's 50th Annual General Assembly; to confirm your presence, please send the following registration fee:</p>
    <p>Registration Fee: <%= number_with_delimiter(@registration.price, :delimiter => ',', :precision => 0) %></p>
    <p>Payment Methods: </p>
    <ol>
      <li> 
        <p>Bank Transfer: </p>
        <p>Bank Name: Metrobank</p>
        <p>Account Name: 1CISP</p>
        <p>Account Number: 232-3-23250315-8</p>
 </li>
      <li> 
        <p>Check Payment: Please make the check payable to 1CISP and mail it to the address mentioned above.</p>
      </li>
    </ol>
  <% else %>
    <p>You have successfully registered for the 50th annual general assembly; We are excited to have you join us for this event. This email serves as a confirmation of your registration, please present this confirmation at the event.</p>
  <% end %>
  <%# <%= content_tag :p, '(49th) Annual General Assembly Meeting and Election on April 15, 2023, Saturday at 9:00 A.M. The meeting will be held at Novotel Manila, Araneta City, General Aguinaldo Ave, Cubao, Quezon City, Metro Manila; and via Zoom (Meeting ID: 857 1289 6787) ' %>
  <% if @guest_type == "Principal Delegate" %>
    <p>
      Your voter's code is <strong> <%= @voter %> </strong>
    </p>
  <%end%>
  
  <p>If you have any questions or require further information about the event, please feel free to contact our event support team at 1cispga@gmail.com or 0922-8437281. We are here to assist you.</p>
  <p>We look forward to welcoming you and creating a memorable experience for all participants.</p> <br>
  <p>The (50th) Annual General Assembly Meeting and Election will take place on April 12-13, 2024. The event will be held at the Manila Marriott Hotel, located at Newport Boulevard, Newport City, Pasay 1309, Metro Manila.</p>
  <% if @registration.award %>
    <p>Congratulations! your one of the winners who can avail the 50th Annual General Assembly merchandise, you can claim your prize at the event. for more information please contact us at 1cisp_ga@gmail.com</p>
  <% end %>
</div>
